channel.title: Server always logs me out
channel.description:
ok so i saw the post by a guy earlier who was having the same problem as i am (when i press log in, it shows me the game then logs me straight back out), he was told to get winrar and java then it will work, it worked for him!
but i already have winrar and java and it still doesnt work for me, any more suggestions?

item.title: Server always logs me out
item.dc:creator: @doom_j doom_j
item.description:
@doom_j wrote:

Make sure you client is compatible with your server meaning you don’t have any ids that would cause a crash in the client like, gfx, interfaces, npcs, items, frames, I have to ask what base are you using because it could also be a anti-leech.
